{"/service/ndnp/mimtptc/batch_mimtptc_bath_ver01/data/sn92063852/00279551321/1958041201/0420.xml":{"full_text":"Cod's Christ Science Universal Messiah World Healing\nV 2SHS T \u00abSI2S\nMonFfiFIVT SurrvMsttr To 3taru Baker Eddy\nMOT TO REPLACE, USURP, O* OESTBOV HER Y.OHTSO. ESTABUSHED LEADERSHIP BUT TO INFORCE THAT L \u00abAOERStUP.ACCO\u00bbmNO TOCHR.ST.n\nh Bring Comfort, P-o-w-t-r, and Liberation from the Deril!-Tbe M-V-t-ll l-TboAotPOrist Adom-Cro \u00a3fo-To tin Oer/y! The Pubht-And Yon!!!\n\"BARUCH ON THE RECESSION\"\n(N.Y. Tribun*, 4/2)\n\"INFINITELY CHEAPER TO PRESERVE PEACE\nTHAN TO FIGHT A WAR\"!\nby Andrew F. Fruehauf, CS.\nModern Christian Science Crusader\nMajor Prophet of \u201cour Father-Mother God, all\nharmonious*' (p. 16, Science and Health with Key te\nthe Scriptures by Mary Baker Eddy) with a world\nmessage and mission, who will\u2014by the grace of God\n\u2014do a Fruehauf-Martin Luther job in thU age!!l\nAnd how! Science Health, our textbook, is God\nLiberator Os The Bible.\nA HIGHER AND TRUER REPRESENTATIVE OF\nGOD THAN THE POPE AT ROME! AND THE\nWRITER IS HIS FRIEND! AND OF HIS PEOPLE.\nTOO!\nJesus \u201cloved righteousness and hated iniquity**)\nThe \"Takewarm\u2019\u2019 live in s \u201cfool\u2019s paradise.\u2019\u2019!\n\n\"WE C-A-N MEET ALL OUR DEFENSE REQUIRE\nMENTS AND STILL PROVIDE ALL OUR NEEDS,\nALTHOUGH MAYBE NOT ALL OUR W-A-N-TS\"\n\"Well spoken words from a man of vision and wisdom\"!\n\u2014N. Y. T ribune editorial.\nTHIS RECESSION IS THE INEVITABLE\nAFTERMATH OF A PERIOD OF INFLATION\nTHAT COULD AT LEAST HAVE BEEN MITIGATED, IF\nNOT PREVENTED.\nBARUCH PROPOSES PAY, PRICE CURB;\nTAX CUT A 'FOLLY'\nYear Freeze Called Aid in Recession\nWarns Senators: Consumer-Revolt\n\nBy Joseph R. Slevin (N.Y. Tribune)\nWASHINGTON, April I\u2014Bernard M. Baruch today said\nit's \"folly\" to talk about cutting taxes to halt the recession.\nHe told the Senate Finance Committee that it would be\n\"uneconomic and immoral\" to reduce the government's\nrevenue; before our defenses are secure and our debt\nmanageable.\"\nvSee BARUCH RECESSION, Page 11)\n\"LABOR'S DAILY\" SUSPENSION\n\u201cLABOR LOSES ONLY DAILY NEWSPAPER\"\nBy Ralph S. White, Editor, Labor's Daily\nSPIRITUALLY BANKRUPT AS IS\nTHE LABOR WORLD!\nGOD VIA HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nPIPE-SMOKING EDITOR WHITE SYMBOLIZES\nTHE SPIRITUAL NAKEDNESS AND SPIRITUAL\nIMPURITY, SPIRITUAL DISHONESTY,\nOF THE ENTIRE LABOR WORLD\nTO FIND CHRISTLIKE, HONEST PERSONS IN THE\nLABOR WORLD\u2014EITHER AMONG ITS LEADERS OR\nRANK AND HAVE GOT TO FIND\nHONEST-TO-GOD CHRISTIAN SCIENTISTS\nTHE HEBREWS, ROMAN CATHOLICS, AND\nPROTESTANTS OF, AND IN, THE LABOR WORLD ARE\nALL PRISONERS OF THE DEVIL EVERY SINGLE\nONE\n(See LABOR DAILY'S SUSPENSION, Page 11)\n(Excerpts from CONGRESSIONAL RECORD\nProceedings and Debates of the 84th Congress,\nFirst Session)\nTHE REAL REUTHER AND HIS PURPOSE\nTHE ESTABLISHMENT OF A SOCIALISTIC\nGOVERNMENT\nRemarks of CLARE E. HOFFMAN of Michigan\nIn The House of Representatives, Tuesday, August 2, 1955\nMr. Hoffman of Michigan. Mr. Speaker, doubtless Wal\nter Reuther is the kind and loving parent, the generous,\nfaithful husband portrayed in recent years in many national,\nly circulated publications.\nBeyond question, he has a political and economic phil\nosophy in which he firmly believes and which he probably\nthinks will be helpful to all mankind.\n(See THE REAL REUTHER, Page 11)\nWalter Reuther, as per Free Press 4/1\n'THE SMEARING HAD ALREADY BEEN DONE\"\nCOD'S DETROIT TRIBUNE ASKS:\nIS THE EVIDENCE BUILDING UP TO MARK\nBOTH REUTHER AND EMIL MAZEY\nAS BENEDICT ARNOLDS AND JUDASES?\nWE SHALL SEE.\nA, W* Sm It\nTHE SMEARING HAD ALREADY BEEN DONE\n(Free Press Editorial, 4/1)\nHaving had Walter Reuther in to answer questions about\nthe UAW's conduct in the Kohler strike, members of the\nMcClellan Committee are now richly ecquainted with Mr.\nReuther's aptitude for changing the subject.\nAsa consequence of his disposition to loom into the dec\nlamatory wild blue yonder, the Senators seem to have found\nout rather less about Mr. Reuther's part in events at Sheboy\ngan than they did about their own iniquity.\n(See THE SMEARING, Page 11)\nPOOR ADLAI STEVENSON\n\"SATAN BOUND\" SOPHISTICATE!\nBECAUSE THE\nDEVIL'S RACKETEERS.\nTHE KREMLIN CRIMINALS' AND SPIRITUAL\nLUNATICS' PROPAGANDA GAINS\nAND DESPITE THE BIBLICAL 40-YEAR RECORD OF\nDECEIT, COLOSSAL BILLION S GRAND LARCENY,\nMASS MURDERS,\u2014ACCORDING TO ADLAI WOULD\nDEPRIVE US OF ANY SHRED OF MORAL LEAD\nERSHIP\"!\u2014C.S.M., 3/31, \"THE Editor and the News,\" by\nErwin D. Canham, Editor of C.S.M.\nPART 2\nDEMOCRATS AND LABOR LEADERS\nWHO ARE NOT CHRISTLIKE CHRISTIAN\nSCIENTISTS. ARE PRISONERS OF THE DEVIL 1,\nEVERY SINGLE ONE!\n(RANK AND FILE, TOO\nREPUBLICANS, TAKE HEED LIKEWISE I\nKNAVES AND FOOLS ARE A NATURAL STATUS\nFOR THE M-Y-T-H-I-C A-L, DEVILISH, ANTI-CHRIST,\nADAM-EVE, MURDEROUS CAIN, JUDAS, KNAVES\nAND FOOLS' EGO AND PSYCHOLOGY OF ALL HUMAN\nBIRTHS !\u2014\"THE GHASTLY FARCE OF MATERIAL\nIso-called] EXISTENCE\"!\u2014p. 272,\u2014MY MASTERPIECE,\nTHE C.S. TEXTBOOK !\u2014IMPERATIVE SAVIOR,\nLIBERATOR, AND PROTECTOR OF THE HOLY\nSCRIPTURES\u2014King James Protestant, MY CHOSEN\nONE! FROM THE INVOLUNTARY, SPIRITUAL\nADULTERY OF THE FOUR EUROPEAN RELIGIOUS\nCRIPPLES AND THE \"SATAN BOUND\" CLERGY,\nTHE NON-CHRIST SCIENTISTS\nEISENHOWER'S FINEST HOUR\n(Excerpts from N. Y. Tribune Editorial)\nNo graver problem confronts the American nation than\nto create a Defense Department which operates \"with top\nefficiency and without friction.\" No other man is as uniquely\nqualified as Dwight D. Eisenhower, the nation's first soldier,\nto bring this about.\n(See EISENHOWER'S HOUR, Page 11)\nGOD'S DETROIT TRIBUNE SUPPORTS\nAMERICAN MOTORS COUP.\n\"PAY-FREEZE PLAN\"!\n(News, 4/3)\n\"UAW ASSAILS AMC PLAN\"\n\"AMC PAY FREEZE SNUBBED\"\n(Times, 4/3)\nMESSRS. GEORGE ROMNEY, President AND\nEDWARD L. CUSHMAN, Vice-President, STAND FAST\nAGAINST THOSE DEVIL'S ADAMS, PLUNDERERS,\nRACKETEERS!\nGOD'S DETROIT TRIBUNE, ADDITIONALLY:\nTHE DEVIL'S DEMOCRATIC-LABOR\n100 BILLION S-T-E-A-L\nHAS ALREADY PUT PACKARD AND KAISER\nFRASER, AND NUMEROUS OTHER MANUFACTURERS\nOUT OF BUSINESS\n(See GOD'S DETROIT TRIBUNE SUPPORTS, Page 11)\n\u201c3 [Negro] Youths Are Jailed\nIn Teacher Stoning\"\nGOD VIA HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nAS THE SHEPHERDS. SO THE SHEEP\nAND THE LAMBS i\nCURSES ON THE DEVIL'S EXPLOITERS\n-PITTSBURGH COURIER AND EBONY\nPROMOTERS OF THE DEVIL'S BILLION RACKETS\n1. S-E-X\u2014ALWAYS OF THE DEVIL !\u2014MARRIAGE,\nA DIVINE INSTRUMENT FOR MORAL AND\nLEGAL CONTROL !\u2014RAMPANT THROUGHOUT\nSOCIETY AND ESPECIALLY IN THE ENTER\nTAINMENT WORLD AND WORLD OF LETTERS!\n2. ALCOHOLIC BEVERAGES I, and\n3. TOBACCO and\n4. DRUG STORE AND HOSPITAL MEDICINES\nPATHETIC CREATIONS OF ADAMS AND EVES STILL\nRUNNING AROUND IN SPIRITUAL DIAPERS' I\u2014\n(See 3 YOUTHS JAILED, Page 11)\n\"7 SENATORS FIGHT TEST OF TOLL TV\"\n(News, 1/28)\nGOD VIA HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nWE STAND UNEQUIVOCALLY FOR TOLL TV!\nTHERE IS NO FREE' TVI\u2014THE PUBLIC PAYS, AND\nPAYS, AND PAYS NOT TOO MUCH WITH MANY\nMERITED ADVERTISED PRODUCTS, BUT IMMENSELY\nTOO MUCH IN THE COST TO HEALTH, HEAVEN,\nHELL, \"LIFE MORE ABUNDANTLY,\" VIA THE DEVIL'S\nFOUR BILLION RACKETS, COMING INTO MIL\nLIONS OF HOMES VIA RADIO AND TV\u2014\n1. SEX\u2014DEVIL'S SOCIAL H-BOMB'\u2014RAMPANT\nTHROUGHOUT SOCIETY AND ESPECIALLY\nIN THE ENTERTAINMENT WORLD AND WORLD\nOF LETTERS!\n(See 7 SENATORS FIGHT TEST, Page 11)\nTribune\nRepresenting \"Our Father-Molher Gods\" eur Divine Publisher\nCrusader For The Invincible Triumphant Divine Rights of Men\nDETROIT, MICHIGAN, SATURDAY, APRIL 12, 1958\nFEAR NO EVIL\nClnit JL* J EU -Aft\nBy Elizabeth Ellington\nBecause it has been made known that the Christ lives,\nwe do not have to go after strange gods. It is through the\nlove of the one God, for His spiritual creation, that Christ\nlives to bless all.\nWhen walking in the light of the directions of Jesus, and\nlooking to our heavenly Father, we do not labor in vain\nwhen solving so called human problems.\nNOW THE ELEVEN DISCIPLES WENT TO GALILEE TO\nWHICH JESUS HAD DIRECTED THEM. AND WHEN THEY\nSAW HIM THEY WORSHIPPED HIM BUT SOME DOUBT-\nED. (MATT. 28:16-17)\nThe law of our Heavenly\nFather, through scientific\nprayerful study, and common\nsense reasoning, easies and\nlightens human burdens, and\nsets mankind on the straight\npathway of walking in the\nlight of Truth.\nThe structure of light and\neverlasting love has always\nbeen here, and will remain\nforever; our job is to claim\nit.\nIt is of great interest to\nnote how the people are turn\ning to God in times of trou\nble unashamed by error.\nScience and Health with\nkey to the Scriptures by\nMary Eddy teaches:\n\"Matter does not express\nSpirit. God is infinite omni\npresent Spirit.\n\u201cIf Spirit is all and is every\nwhere, what and where is\nmatter? Remember that\nTRUTH is greater than error,\n50th ANNIVERSARY C. MONITOR\n\"PAGEANT OF FIVE DECADES 3rd\"\nBy Edwin D. Canham, Editor of Tha C. S. Monitor\nBy its third docada, Tha Christian Scianca Monitor was\nwall praparad to faca tha challengas of worldwida economic\ncollapse and tha aggressive surge of totalitarianism.\nTha paper had detected tha clear need of a sounder\nworld economic foundation and a firmer basis on which\npeace could be enforced. It was well equipped for tha\ntroubles of late 1929, for it had warned of many dangers\nwhich could have been avoided. Its basic attitude, as the\ndepression deepened, was to isolate the causes of world\neconomic unbalance and to define remedies for them.\n(See 50TH ANNIVERSARY, Page 2)\n\"EAST IS BATTERED 2d DAY\"\nGOD VIA HIS DETROIT TRIBUNEt\nC S. HQ., BOSTON, ATTENTION:\nBETTER 'LAY OFF' THAT \"LAVENDER KID ZEAL\"\n(I to Mrs. Eddy, to you) AND ALLOW WARRIOR\nANGEL, MICHAEL, TO WAGE THE SPIRITUAL \"WAR\nFARE WITH THE WORLD [Adam-Eve MYTH\nTHE FLESH, AND THE DEVIL\"\n\"THE FATHER'S BUSINESS\"\u2014THE R-EA-L WORK\nOF ALL RACES AND PEOPLES, ALL THE TIME I\u2014\nMUST NOT BE EMASCULATED IN SUCH NAIVE\nLANGUAGE, MERELY THE REFLECTION OF DIVINE\n(See EAST IS BATTERED, Page 2)\nUAW STRIKE HEADLINES\u2014\n\"TELL INDIANA STRIKE TERROR\"\n\"ADMIT UAW SENT GOON SQUADS\nTO PERFECT CIRCLE\"\n(Chicago Tribune, 4/2)\n\n\"HOW VIOLENCE LOOKED DURING INDIANA STRIKE''\n\"TRIBUNE RECALLS NEWS OF LAWLESSNESS\"\n(Chicago Tribune, 4/2)\n\n\"PERFECT CIRCLE STRIKE IS ISSUE\"\n\"FIRM, UAW SWAP CHARGES AT PROBE\"\nft (Free Pre**, 4/1)\n\n\"PROBERS TOLD OF VIOLENCE\"\n(Detroit Time*, 4/1)\n\n\"BLAME UAW'S HIGH BRASS FOR VIOLENCE\"\n\"OFFICIALS TELL OF INDIANA STRIKE\"\n(Chicago Tribune)\n\n\"UNION BOSSES ON VIEW\"\n(Chicago Tribune, 4/1, p. 2)\n\n\"DSR MEN JEER UNION LEADERS\"\n(N*w\u00ab, 1/31. P- 21\n\n\"HE SHOOK UP THE DSR UNION\"\n(Detroit Time*, p- 2)\n\u2022_ e\n\"01* MEN JEER CHIEP; SSOOO MORE MISSING\"\nINm, 1/11, P- 21\nDETROIT\nand we cannot put the\ngreater into the less. SOLI.\nIS SPIRIT, and Spirit is\ngreater than body. If Spirit\nwere once within the body,\nSpirit would be finite, and\ntherefore could not be\nSpirit.\" (S H, page 223)\n\nWORK FOR GOOD\nThe appearance of the\nChrist Spirit in all human\naffairs does away with the\nerrors and falsity, as man\nkind learns to listen to the\nVoice of Truth and Love.\nDivine learning to listen, may\nbe done gradually, yet, it\nhas its right place in the\nconsciousness of men, and\nwomen who are looking for\nthe full source of \"Life more\nabundantly.\" Christ proved\nGod to be that full source\nof lift for the entire uni\n(Continued on Page 4)","height":"28149","width":"18642"}}
